Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! I'm perfectly fine now!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And how about him?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Him"?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing great.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking care\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}of Manaka yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But lemme say this.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Surface people have got no business\Nconcerning themselves with the ocean village.{}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}! That was really rude of you!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.99,0:04:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard all about it! Thanks to him,\Nyou had a rough time, right?{possible split}{}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not true.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't the surface people\Nput you through a lot?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's guilty by association!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... Tsumugu{-kun} saved me!{possible split}{}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tsu-mu-gu{-kun}"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-Why are you getting so upset?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting so\Nbuddy-buddy with him?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, then{replace}... Mr. Tsumugu{ Tsumugu... -san}?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.09,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I don't know his last name!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y{ou know, y}ou've been acting weird{ly} lately, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so angry!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.89,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.63,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I messed up!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Messed up what?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu{-kun} saved me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.68,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though Hii{-kun}\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}worried about me a lot too,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I got mad at him.{"accused" is literal}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I really messed up!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.85,0:05:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari was really worried\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}about you, Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii{-chan}.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really worried.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.37,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though his Ena was dry\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}and he couldn't breathe that well,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,he was determined to find you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari isn't really mad at you,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so try not to act so afraid of him, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll only annoy him {even }more.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii{-chan}, how do you know all this?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,About how both of us feel, I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.84,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It must be because I've known you{ guys/two} since we were really young.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hold it right there, you sea slug!{supposed to be a mild insult so hf}{}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're those kids from the other day...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that lady?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What lady?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know her?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my older sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! You octopus head!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"O-Octopus"?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He {replace}was acting real close{wasn't even using honorifics} with her.{without honorific}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They've gotta be boyfriend\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}and girlfriend, Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.11,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.11,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't really know\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}what's going on here,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but shouldn't you two be in school?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teacher's gonna get mad—{}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a brat, you brat!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to hear\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}that from some brat.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've brought\Nbackup, you coward!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, {\i1}you're{\i0} one to talk.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}picking on little kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Get your fishy-smelly\Nhands away from me!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.15,0:07:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you rice!{just another of these mild insults. theyre supposed to sound sort of ridiculous. they sound sorta funny and random in japanese}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. That's it for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who here wants to try\Nmaking a Wooden Maiden?{joushi means 'girl'.}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a "Wooden Maiden"?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the doll we{'d} send off\Nin the Boatdrift Ceremony?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When we{ landlubbers} first started performing\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}the Boatdrift Ceremony,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.48,0:07:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a girl would be sent off on a boat\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}as a sacrifice to the sea god.
