Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, instead of an actual girl,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.64,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we send off a carved doll\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}called a Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do {\i1}we{\i0} gotta make\Nthe Wooden Maidens?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't the adults supposed\Nto be doing this kinda stuff?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I heard they're not doing\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}the Boatdrift Ceremony this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.22,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which is why we were thinking of doing something\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}like a voluntary Boatdrift Ceremony at our school.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, calm down.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isn't there anyone who wants to do it?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's it gotta be {\i1}us{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something the surface people\Nare supposed to do!{check timing}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, {if that's (really) how you feel}you shouldn't have volunteered.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.84,0:08:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The surface people don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've gotta\Nkeep an eye on 'em.{he explicitly says we}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did {\i1}you{\i0} volunteer for this?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My family are fishermen.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.49,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We live off the sea, so the Boatdrift Ceremony is my {chance to give}way of giving something back to it{ the sea}.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} actually exists.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sort of like a\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}pervy old man, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say he's kind of in between\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}an old man and a young guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So he {\i1}does{\i0} exist.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about saltflake snow?{this is a pretty cool tl}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, when salt falls down like snow.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and if spirit fire\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}can burn underwater,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then how do you {actually }get it to go out?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu{-kun}, you're really\Nrather knowledgeable!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About Shioshishio, I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On days when the sun's really bright
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the light refracts in the right way,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{there are times when }you can sometimes catch a glimpse\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}of the ocean village.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,White roofs reflect\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}light between the swells.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And almost like the sound\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}of the waves themselves,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.01,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear singing drifting up—\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}sometimes far, sometimes near.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.09,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the ocean village.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.99,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised someone on the surface\Ncares so much about our village!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's about time for you sea kiddos\Nto head home, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can take it from here.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.82,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get home safely!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Teach{Sensei}.{credited as "homeroom teacher", sorry}{T.T}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to ask of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Our teacher{Sensei} just called us "sea kiddos"!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard! It was actually kind of cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I admit he doesn't seem like a bad guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.81,0:10:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even so...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Akari{-san}?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She k-k-k-ki—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.90,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, shh!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.74,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She never even mentioned having one!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.52,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And to top it off, it's a\Nguy from the surface?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Akari's{Akari-san is} just about old enough\Nto get married, huh?{getting to the age where she's old enough to get married.}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's planning\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}to leave the village.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it'd work out\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}with a guy from the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they got married,\Nshe'd end up coming right back.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible? Why not?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not possible!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.04,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Akari{-san} looks like she's\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}going to be a great mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course she wouldn't {end up }\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}come right back.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get into a relationship\Nwith someone from the surface,{its a big vague. i suppose it strongly implies marriage, but it doesnt necessarily have to be}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you get permanently\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}banished from the village.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Banished"?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! That's awful.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you yelling at {\i1}me{\i0} for?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.83,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that rule's been around\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}for quite some time.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the first\N{\i1}I've{\i0} ever heard of it!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But Satsuki{-san} from the candy store
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and Koji{-niisan} from Hara{-san}'s family
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,went up to the surface and never came back, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought that the people who didn't come back
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,discarded{threw away} the sea and\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}didn't {\i1}want{\i0} to come back{ because they threw away the sea}.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.82,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with wanting to be{come} family\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}with someone who's precious to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful thing!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.32,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To chase them out of the sea like that...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.21,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean... you're thinking of\Ngetting with a guy from the surface, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quit it!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it when you say\Nperverted things, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And {}I{} hate it when {\i1}you{\i0} say\Nperverted things, Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't say anything perverted!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You did too!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you've been\Ngrossing me out a lot lately!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand how you feel,\Nbut don't you think you went too—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you "understand"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you get off, always\Npretending to be so grown-up?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You act like such a know-it-all.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you know about me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get so angry.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.91,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I can understand why\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}you'd be irritated with Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is with them?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeating that they understand\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}like a broken record...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while even I...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}don't really understand {exactly }how I'm feeling.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This saltflake snow is pretty intense...{the saltflake snow that's there. "a lot of saltflake snow fell"}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,especially since no one\Nbothers cleaning it up.{implied: so a lot piles up}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been nice if we could've stayed at Namiji Middle School.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{I guess }Even you think about things like that sometimes, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.88,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like wanting to\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}stay here forever, I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.81,0:14:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's not that I don't like\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}the people on the surface...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I want to\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}stay in the sea forever.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.97,0:14:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With Manaka and you... and Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.09,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you just want to stay here because\Nfeeling like that is what's comfortable{ for you}?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.74,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you long for other places,\Nlife starts to get harder{ for you}.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.81,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that Manaka\Nwas the first one of us
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the first step outta here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiyoshi, Ukita, Kamon...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihara Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.51,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihara{-kun}, Kihara{-kun}, Kihara{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Hii{-kun} won't get angry anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihara{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If they got your DNA, it sucks to be them.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.80,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You idiot! You saw the footage!\NIt was super cute!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Akari...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And this is our baby!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My, isn't she cute! Does she\Nresemble you more?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, it's a girl! I'm so envious.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I have a kid,\NI want it to be a girl, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.82,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, she might have her father's eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.92,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a younger sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lately, she started mimicking me.\NHave you seen her do it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was totally bummed when you came out.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I haven't, but how does she mimic you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.84,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am envious...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.52,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When I say "me," she says it back, and\Nwhen I say "mo," she says that back too!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But if I say "memo"—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get into a relationship with\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}someone from the surface,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you get permanently\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}banished from the village.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And she's only gonna continue\Nto grow. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, it's a lot of work,\Nbut every day is a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Spoken like a true mo—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that girl from Shioshishio?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.09,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.81,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A guy from the surface, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.07,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just... wanted to protect her.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to protect her like Ena does.{like ena protects the wearer in general}{I guess I like the misreading, now that I think about it.}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.43,0:17:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to protect her from anything\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r\i1}and everything that could{'ve} hurt her.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.07,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...{Scene straight out of The Little Mermaid...}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.09,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wants to just discard all that?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To discard everything...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and go to a different world...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how big the kimono should be.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.95,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumu—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.19,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kihara{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.22,0:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We were wondering how wide around\Nthe waist the Wooden Maiden is.{}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme check.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it still sounds perverted
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I used his last name.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How's he doing today?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be sleeping...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.87,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixty-five centimeters.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.69,0:18:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Manaka really {\i0}does{\i1} like him{Kihara-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.39,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, if Manaka's\Never out of the picture,{ep01}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'll{\i0} be the one by his{Hikari's} side.{ep01}
