Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they used\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}to keep carp there.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed some garbage.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little small for\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}four people to get in, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Four people"?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.18,0:19:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it'd get annoying always\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}having to worry about the time{ while you're working}.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And {replace}Teach{Sensei} said it'd be fine to use this{ as well}.{}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're going to\Nmake a pond{watering hole} just for us?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be a bother?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, not at all! Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.63,0:19:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl with the really round eyes...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope her fish is happy about it, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Her fish?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.59,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be so\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}kind to Manaka anymore.
