Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you,{comma splice of a sort, but maa ii ka} please curse me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it you wanna be cursed again?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.73,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, w-well...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it hurts to lie.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why lie, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it like that,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.57,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Up till now, you've always had\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}someone protecting you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.25,0:20:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, Chisaki, Kaname...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.38,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've just kept floundering\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}along behind them.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.21,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, you're about to go somewhere\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}they can't protect you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.56,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe you need a little lie\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}or two to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here, Akari.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.06,0:20:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have you explain everything\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}in front of {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.56,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! I'll tell my dad myself!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.14,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.08,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't concern you two.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.00,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay out of—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. It's about time\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}they found out too.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.05,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They should find out just what happens\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}when you break the rules of this village.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.13,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "what happens"?{What are you talking about?!}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally here, Head Priest.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari is seeing a guy on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone saw them!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you all to leave for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.96,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Head Priest...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.36,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will talk to Akari myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Head Priest, this is a problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.10,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone from your own family\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}leaves for the surface,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's gonna look really bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.
